{"id": "1411661755691569212", "channel_id": "1411661755691569212", "type": 0, "author_id": "591147324185772033", "author_name": "gisstar", "author_bot": false, "content": "the Wheel of Destiny \"Heart of Silver\" have strange wording leading to misunderstanding of its effect, does the 'gain 1.5% of the wielder's STR' mean that it increase the current STR stacks by 1.5% like Miryam's Posse? or does it scale off something else and this is just a mistranslation?", "timestamp": "2025-08-31T10:39:49.964000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1411661755909804162", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 296226, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1411661755691569212/1411661755909804162/image.png?ex=69cc4d36&is=69cafbb6&hm=61920873cd25cfaf4e4375487617afec45895536a901a437a029fcdfcd2d60e7&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1411661755691569212", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Heart of Silver's unclear effect", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785"]}
{"id": "1411718951364202700", "channel_id": "1411718951364202700", "type": 0, "author_id": "532778652337700896", "author_name": "oct3000", "author_bot": false, "content": "https://youtu.be/n86XuBrmPt4?si=vtc8H8UBG8xh92Q2\n有錄影片為證\n\n一啟效果: 基礎防禦在手牌 \"追加一張\" 腺體分裂\n實際效果是 基礎防禦會 \"抽一張\" 腺體分裂\n會影響開局體驗，先打防禦就只會上盾而已。", "timestamp": "2025-08-31T14:27:06.475000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1411718951850873023", "filename": "322870d3e736df4bae178584e05b85d2.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 78203, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1411718951364202700/1411718951850873023/322870d3e736df4bae178584e05b85d2.png?ex=69cbd9ba&is=69ca883a&hm=746c353965d94a235a8b16d17bb66a11e0e6a949671ba25f8a10fcbf24efba5a&"}, {"id": "1411718952245002332", "filename": "b72fa5e8c4a1b9b7d7b14f2fc9c53706.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 123973, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1411718951364202700/1411718952245002332/b72fa5e8c4a1b9b7d7b14f2fc9c53706.png?ex=69cbd9ba&is=69ca883a&hm=a95d8a69a1bb2ed47bc88a7fb507d1771f51bf89d02849ec5f28dc5868ce24ea&"}], "embeds": [{"type": "video", "title": "aurita_bug", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n86XuBrmPt4", "description": ""}], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1411718951364202700", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」日服BUG可以在這底回報嗎", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1411603734978625536", "channel_id": "1411603734978625536", "type": 0, "author_id": "244028747999608832", "author_name": "vxvendetta", "author_bot": false, "content": "The description of the PARADOX covenant make you believe that even if the aliemus cap is now 120, the exalt cost is still 100, so, in theory, after exalting you should still have 20 aliemus. But in reality, when you exalt you use all the aliemus and remain at 0.\nIs this a bug or intended? \nCan the description be adjusted to reflect the actual functionality?", "timestamp": "2025-08-31T06:49:16.748000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-08-31T06:49:35.406000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1411603735515238500", "filename": "aawds.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 29245, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1411603734978625536/1411603735515238500/aawds.JPG?ex=69cc172c&is=69cac5ac&hm=969ccff70f2eb0b1ed366bc53d229d56afe1577160aba36f66a8a209d19f5273&"}, {"id": "1411603735897182229", "filename": "Captuasdfsdfre.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 28550, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1411603734978625536/1411603735897182229/Captuasdfsdfre.JPG?ex=69cc172c&is=69cac5ac&hm=a25c5efff838be74f8ce2da9924d4bd4361fb9f2638105a560a2a5254a5e69c7&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1411603734978625536", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」PARADOX mistranslation \\bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1411606617580896266", "channel_id": "1411603734978625536", "type": 0, "author_id": "88644018673582080", "author_name": "arkaether", "author_bot": false, "content": "Yes, that is a bug! I have confirmed via the original Chinese text that the correct translation for this effect is \"Increase Aliemus Cap and Exalt Aliemus Consumption by 20\". I have submitted it as a fix and it should hopefully be updated at some point.", "timestamp": "2025-08-31T07:00:44.014000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1411603734978625536", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」PARADOX mistranslation \\bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
