{"id": "1411811415936991313", "channel_id": "1411811415936991313", "type": 0, "author_id": "478214049033879563", "author_name": "yannic2112", "author_bot": false, "content": "I suggest adding a testing stage where you can test your units. For example if I have 2 wheels and wonder which is better for a unit, then I could just go to that stage and test it out. This means that you would be able to choose freely on how many units you field (1-4). Additionally, if there would be enough resources from the dev team, maybe also let us choose what level the opponents are on and which opponents we are up agains. But for now, just a general stage for testing would be nice.", "timestamp": "2025-08-31T20:34:31.747000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "☝️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1411811415936991313", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Testing stage", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1411822310071074856", "channel_id": "1411811415936991313", "type": 0, "author_id": "244028747999608832", "author_name": "vxvendetta", "author_bot": false, "content": "This can be useful, I normally use farming stages to do tests, but that is not always ideal, plus having the ability to be able to test with specific enemys and use Astral Realm rules without spending resources would be appreciated.", "timestamp": "2025-08-31T21:17:49.111000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-08-31T21:18:07.987000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1411811415936991313", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Testing stage", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
